column4: NSLOCTEXT("[D7ED791644474F02E0DAE4B000D3151A]", "1CD2E08D4F0E95ADEDA3E2B46C543030", "Hey, there\'s a stone tablet. Let\'s see...")
NSLOCTEXT("[D7ED791644474F02E0DAE4B000D3151A]", "92DF785C4A01B37F89A8FD8538990FFE", "It says Leomon. I can\'t read the rest.")
NSLOCTEXT("[D7ED791644474F02E0DAE4B000D3151A]", "A47B77444F7BB7106F12DD8EF958114E", "I can understand speech, but not writing...")
NSLOCTEXT("[D7ED791644474F02E0DAE4B000D3151A]", "A40D0F5045EBBEE38E2FB594D3C7C3E0", "Oops, I have to throw something away.")
